So the backup troops
are already here, huh?

00:00:38.744 --> 00:00:39.680
[exhales sharply]

00:00:41.382 --> 00:00:42.819
[Erika] Terrorists?

00:00:42.886 --> 00:00:45.925
So that means we can kick
their butts no questions asked,

00:00:45.992 --> 00:00:47.027
am I right?

00:00:47.094 --> 00:00:48.096
Since they're not students,

00:00:48.163 --> 00:00:49.465
no need to hold back.

00:00:49.533 --> 00:00:50.602
[chuckles]

00:00:50.668 --> 00:00:51.971
By the way, Erika,

00:00:52.037 --> 00:00:53.574
did you spot
any other intruders?

00:00:53.641 --> 00:00:55.645
[Haruka] Their actual target
is the library.

00:00:56.780 --> 00:00:57.816
[Tatsuya] Counselor Ono?

00:00:57.882 --> 00:01:00.521
Attacking you here
was simply a diversion.

00:01:01.289 --> 00:01:04.095
[Haruka] Their primary team
already went inside.

00:01:04.462 --> 00:01:06.332
Sayaka Mibu is there, too.

00:01:06.734 --> 00:01:07.736
After this is all over,

00:01:07.802 --> 00:01:09.706
do you mind explaining
what's going on?

00:01:09.773 --> 00:01:11.042
I'm afraid not.

00:01:12.411 --> 00:01:14.282
At least,
that's what I'd like to say.

00:01:14.883 --> 00:01:16.720
Although, I'm guessing
you won't accept that.

00:01:17.689 --> 00:01:18.658
[Haruka] If I did,

00:01:18.724 --> 00:01:21.129
would you be so kind
as to do me a favor?

00:01:21.195 --> 00:01:22.431
What's the favor?

00:01:23.668 --> 00:01:24.903
[grunts]

00:01:25.772 --> 00:01:28.476
I'm asking this of you
as Haruka Ono, the counselor.

00:01:28.844 --> 00:01:30.080
‐ [grunts]
‐ [Haruka] I want you to give

00:01:30.147 --> 00:01:32.251
Miss Mibu a chance, Tatsuya.

00:01:33.320 --> 00:01:34.790
<i>Ever since the previous year,</i>

00:01:34.856 --> 00:01:36.326
<i>I've noticed she's</i>
<i>been struggling</i>

00:01:36.392 --> 00:01:38.597
<i>to reconcile the gap between</i>
<i>her kendo skills</i>

00:01:38.664 --> 00:01:40.367
<i>and the course two evaluation.</i>

00:01:41.537 --> 00:01:43.139
I guess it was too tall
of a task

00:01:43.206 --> 00:01:44.643
for me to take on.

00:01:44.710 --> 00:01:47.348
She ended up playing right into
those people's hands.

00:01:47.949 --> 00:01:49.051
So would you‐‐

00:01:49.118 --> 00:01:50.053
[Tatsuya] You're too forgiving.

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:51.757
‐ [gasps]
‐ Miyuki, let's go.

00:01:51.824 --> 00:01:52.859
Okay.

00:01:52.926 --> 00:01:54.095
Tatsuya, wait a sec!

00:01:54.462 --> 00:01:56.366
Don't you think you're being
a little callous?

00:01:58.403 --> 00:02:01.910
Leo, you won't be the only one
of us getting hurt thanks

00:02:01.977 --> 00:02:03.046
to gullibility.

00:02:03.113 --> 00:02:04.415
[gasps]

00:02:05.217 --> 00:02:06.352
[exhales]

00:02:07.822 --> 00:02:09.191
[both gasping]

00:02:09.258 --> 00:02:11.295
Hey, wait a sec!
Tatsuya!

00:02:13.099 --> 00:02:14.135
[snarls]

00:02:14.201 --> 00:02:15.137
[gasps]

00:02:15.203 --> 00:02:16.540
Miyuki!
[grunts]

